  "title": "Desolation",
  "description": "Wildfires bring both destruction and renewal.",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eZ32Gbw.png\" alt=\"Desolation for Fabric 1.21\" width=\"1280\" height=\"400\" /></strong></span></p>\n<!--<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img title=\"Requires Fabric API\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"149\" height=\"50\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/trinkets\"><img title=\"Requires Trinkets API\" bsrc=\"https://i.imgur.com/xDmzB7w.png\" width=\"149\" height=\"50\" /></a></div>-->\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ihiJYm2.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1600\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Features:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A new biome, the Charred Forest, including several variants.</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Two new mobs: the Ash Scuttler and the Blackened.</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">One new wood type, Charred Wood, and all its associated blocks.</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Useful new resources to collect, including ash and cinderfruit.</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">New protective equipment (masks and goggles).</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A powerful new potion to brew.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Screenshots:</strong></span></p>\n<p><br/><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/403/746/2021-10-25_03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"596\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/403/748/2021-03-20_02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"596\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/403/747/2021-03-20_02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"596\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/404/453/2021-10-29_06.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"596\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ihiJYm2.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1600\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>My other mods:</strong><br /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mob-blindness\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/39e47caJ/icon.png\" width=\"75\" height=\"75\" /><br /><strong>Mob Blindness</strong> (Fabric 1.16/1.17)</a></p>\n</div>",
